msgid "Throughout this scenario, you may be instructed to place new locations on top of existing ones. When a location is placed on top of a location that is already in play, it takes its place. All tokens, attachments, investigators, enemies, and other cards at the former location are considered to now be at the new location (they have not ΟΔβ²§≈™movedΟΔβ²§¬ùΟΔβ²§βÄùthe location simply changed). If a location leaves play and there is another location underneath it, that location takes its place. All tokens, attachments, investigators, enemies, and other cards at the location leaving play are considered to now be at the former location."
msgstr "Ao longo deste cenΟΓrio, vocΟΣ pode receber instruΟßΟΒes para colocar novos locais em cima dos jΟΓ existentes. Quando um local Ο© colocado em cima de outro local que jΟΓ estΟΓ em jogo, ele toma o lugar do antigo local. Todas as fichas, anexos, investigadores, inimigos e outras cartas que estavam no antigo local sΟΘo consideradas agora no novo local (nenhum desses elementos se moveu βÄî simplesmente o local mudou). Se um local sair de jogo e houver outro local embaixo dele, o antigo local toma o lugar dele. Todas as fichas, anexos, investigadores, inimigos e outras cartas que estavam no local que saiu de jogo sΟΘo consideradas agora no antigo local."

